	* *: create gnome-2-2 branch and commit following patch to HEAD
	* bonobo/bonobo-ui-sync-toolbar.c: Move _set_border_width () call
	* bonobo/bonobo-ui-toolbar.c: Add shadow_type style property, to match
	GtkToolbar drawing
	
